<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Privacy Policy — Young Mothers' Day Care'</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f7f8fb;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --muted: #6b7280;
            --accent: #0b74de
        }

        body {
            font-family: Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,"Helvetica Neue",Arial;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: #111
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 48px auto;
            padding: 24px
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(16,24,40,0.06);
            padding: 32px
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.6rem
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin: 20px 0 8px
        }

        p, li {
            color: #111;
            margin: 8px 0
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 1.1rem
        }

        .muted {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem
        }

        .foot {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eef2f7;
            padding-top: 16px;
            color: var(--muted)
        }

        code {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: monospace
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="container">
        <article class="card">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="muted">Last Updated: <strong>12/12/2025</strong></p>
            <p>Young Mothers' Day Care Belfast values your privacy. We only collect the information needed to provide our services, such as your name and contact details.</p>
            <p>We do not sell your information. It may be shared only with trusted service providers or if required by law.</p>
            <p>Your information is kept secure. You may request to view or delete your information at any time.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, contact us on our contact us page </p>
        </article>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
